Sentencas: It is a big challenge to develop composite materials with high catalytic activity and stability in a fast and simple way in the field of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: One-pot synthesis Pr6O11 decorated Pr2CuO4 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this paper, Pr2CuO4Pr6O11 composites are prepared by a novel one-pot synthesis method.
Titulo: One-pot synthesis Pr6O11 decorated Pr2CuO4 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The temperature dependent phase evolution of the composite material is studied, and the oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) properties are characterized in detail by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy combining with the distribution of relaxation time analysis.
Titulo: One-pot synthesis Pr6O11 decorated Pr2CuO4 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The decoration of Pr6O11 effectively inhibits the coarsening of Pr2CuO4 particles, enlarging the specific surface area and thereby promoting the oxygen adsorption capability of the composite cathode.
Titulo: One-pot synthesis Pr6O11 decorated Pr2CuO4 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Compared to Pr2CuO4, the polarization resistance of Pr2CuO4-20%Pr6O11 is 0.07 U cm2 at 700 degrees C, and the power (current) density reachs to 0.97 W cm-2 (1.62 A cm-2) at 0.6 V for the anode supported fuel cell.
Titulo: One-pot synthesis Pr6O11 decorated Pr2CuO4 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This result proves that one-pot synthesis method is an effective strategy to design cathode materials with high activity, and Pr2CuO4-20%Pr6O11 is potential cathode material for SOFC.
Titulo: One-pot synthesis Pr6O11 decorated Pr2CuO4 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cells
